<section class="brand--cabinet-office brand__border-color organisation__brand-border-top organisation__section-wrap organisation__margin-bottom" id="what-we-do">
  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">What Civil Service Reform does</h2>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-row">
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
    
          <p></p>
<div class="govspeak">
<p>Civil Service Reform sets out a series of specific and practical actions for reform which is leading to real changes for the Civil Service.</p>

<p><abbr title="Civil Service Reform">CSR</abbr> is part of the <a class="brand__color" href="/government/organisations/civil-service">Civil Service</a>.</p>
</div>

          <p>
            <a href="/government/organisations/civil-service-reform/about" class="brand__color">
              Read more about what we do
            </a>
          </p>

</div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>



